{"id":2218334,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC8yMjE4MzM0","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/2218334","title":"IDOR vulnerability in unreleased HackerOne Copilot feature","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","severity_rating":"medium","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2023-10-20T21:58:50.328Z","submitted_at":"2023-10-20T21:58:50.535Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"bebiks","url":"/bebiks","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/on7l5c1vrq7t7mduui8ijpbkvqui/c8a1698ff707a5e3e8a91a3484838363845daac68cb82c86d55c9e2d44d67b67"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":true,"verified":true,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":13,"url":"https://hackerone.com/security","handle":"security","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/000/013/fa942b9b1cbf4faf37482bf68458e1195aab9c02_original.png/235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/000/013/fa942b9b1cbf4faf37482bf68458e1195aab9c02_original.png/3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"open","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"HackerOne","twitter_handle":"Hacker0x01","website":"https://hackerone.com","about":"Vulnerability disclosure should be safe, transparent, and rewarding."}},"has_bounty?":true,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":true,"disclosed_at":"2023-10-25T23:17:15.093Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2023-10-25T23:17:14.941Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2023-10-25T23:12:27.507Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"**Summary:**\nHello HackerOne security team :-)\nFor a while now I have been monitoring H1 js files. I've just noticed some new GraphQL queries about `HackerOne Copilot`. While this feature has not yet been released, the vulnerability must be fixed.\n`DestroyLlmConversation` GraphQL mutation is vulnerable to IDOR.\n\n### Steps To Reproduce\n1. Navigate to `https://hackerone.com/opportunities/all`\n2. Execute this JS command to show `Hackerone Copilot` GUI\n```javascript\ndocument.querySelectorAll('div').forEach(e =\u003e {\n    e.classList.remove('hidden');\n    e.classList.remove('dark:text-white');\n});\n```\n{F2790650}\n3. Hackerone Copilot GUI will appear, here you can create a new conversation. Looks like you can't talk to LLM at the moment.\n4. After creating a new conversation, look for `\"operationName\":\"NewConversation\",` graphql request in your `Proxy History` and store somewhere the value of `data.newConversation.llm_conversation.id` from the response.\n5. From the second (attacker) account, send the following graphql request:\n```json\n{\"operationName\":\"DestroyLlmConversation\",\"variables\":{\"llmConversationId\":\"#\"},\"query\":\"\\n  mutation DestroyLlmConversation($llmConversationId: ID!) {\\n    destroyConversation(input: { llm_conversation_id: $llmConversationId }) {\\n      destroyed\\n    }\\n  }\\n\"}\n```\n6. Go back to the victim account, refresh the page, execute the script again, and notice that the conversation is gone.\n\n## Impact\n\nThis vulnerability allows the attacker to remove any LLM conversation in the unreleased `HackerOne Copilot` feature. This feature has not been released yet although this might still be vulnerable in the future when this feature is released.","weakness":{"id":55,"name":"Insecure Direct Object Reference (IDOR)"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":2790650,"file_name":"image.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/s8m5nug1calsc5393ifk9sxiknxs?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22image.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27image.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQ2AOOH4U7%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T073013Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIDXUhfeWK%2F%2FgENm9NZ3vJzC%2BnF6lwiJ4i9gqLUzKwZVFAiEAqNndjHUjMVISdSuaLhwLPjQa%2FIH2LzdMjZcycVtkeSsqugUI8P%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDJRQoaV6SZf5Se5G0iqOBYxfpGtkhbE9QQdD%2FoMEOG2uucVDJUtWQpOhBK8QnOlBv%2F%2B4KMzU8PAz9xxB7%2FEHJCTA7X3G6UWoKUy7o1IT2zkcq1vnXjPW%2Fm77LDp5fxb2KHJX0EDW4mxa4qT7EK74KxZ8Gl8AImj8Yh9PsAL%2FAWp41zi%2Fx0H2w5cP50950crTfSXQsWXhlz0V0YmstfoE5eBurht7Ba%2Bct8SbxKew%2BgPRECgB7ibtWGkcSiRF93TBxoDyqodvARjWaKV2NWHEJi0clK6t6W4I8lwKU1%2B40sW0aCkiM%2Ffs7mMN%2F5E1xxPKGUVJ6Ed%2BCSE6rhceECyJyn1oGApliNJ7TjPNS47gc%2BQc6zotYmQOS3sxvRTS6kKyqRFtWBolm6JuGQwZ8%2BvfrYECrDuYYPbmQCqBC1UWXAkNO9YoDZPkUI5Q1nQC27%2F9fOE28%2FuxzrZcZloFLhimKyCo7SSOcIzngf2Mx%2FMEw6gUIaz8T5tr%2BUcB%2FcnMOcLw8e2QQIDzxfF0iVnEMzarD2r2ia7LES46skuOWR%2BIiV696SgRmdVU1ORUmQ7QBOSg%2BaQwLm4T6gwo1oGmjZFHVDjpNCuPNbKxF4VKunW3mav1pdgizeawjPDWdWEzOAUv88bViGehRs%2FwPeU2X7xUdbR9gIaxGzjcOdiSOib3qxg4pIWRWPlYu5baRR%2FyLObR5KQ9BmSIM03JLHDv%2FxEBchpcyJUegg8wMGsL9SghKCKlbg3ku9r1f9HgFZVZC2xXpVJlIV%2Fo1x1Ny4QcP59gZwcRORFDuig4HUDAoy4kZg20b%2FP0TDZJH7CmWvkNmgLU%2FGjQZMtfq2T3GeWiizjjPgZHYAEbz74mtrOHkg73iJA078v8UmDIvU0A9UDe7TCc1sbPBjqxAZfWVwTln0NxwzBRF7P%2BW6UNvywWEDG2Meis5GPhqVffyO5j6IAOLQurV0pDtRgSuvLnxEBH2nBtlXCG%2BOphnjN6Ucn3ntz18fFTFhO%2BhvJbrThsxKzS5XGOoSahF3eQVSmqOqrEwyKulkSYZG